na.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港親共商店地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f3f589de\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe33ca4f718246ffa33c7e7bf328e0fea530dbf","tid":1245632,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b22fc8f57e85fa49b115da584d5bdebc565c04eb","tid":1245632,"uid":217844,"like":376,"dislike":4,"score":372,"citedBy":3,"re